prometheus-cvmfs-exporter (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of prometheus-cvmfs-exporter
  * Prometheus exporter for CVMFS client monitoring
  * Includes systemd service and socket files for service management
  * Supports both legacy and modern CVMFS versions (>= 2.13.2)
  * Configurable repository discovery methods (findmnt vs cvmfs_config)
  * Comprehensive metrics collection including:
    - Cache hit rates and sizes
    - Download statistics and performance
    - Repository status and configuration
    - Proxy usage and performance metrics
    - System resource usage by CVMFS processes
  * HTTP header support for direct web serving
  * Secure systemd service configuration with resource limits

 -- Package Maintainer <maintainer@example.com>  Mon, 01 Jan 2024 12:00:00 +0000
